default_page_post_title: Thanks for visiting my fundraising page!
default_page_post_body:
Please help me support The CHIditarod Foundation by making a donation through my page. The process is fast, easy and secure. Thanks so much for your support.

Please also feel free to share this page with your equally generous friends, and don't forget about company matching - if you can double your money, we'll double-appreciate it.
default_team_appeal: Help our team raise money for The CHIditarod XII
default_team_post_body:
Our individual team members have combined digital forces to create this awesome fundraising team. Together we will raise more money for The CHIditarod Foundation than we ever could alone!


Want to help us support local non-profits fighting hunger in innovative ways?


Support by making a donation to our team. The process is fast, easy, and secure... and you can be sure that it will benefit a great cause!


Come join the squad!


team-work [teem-wurk] noun


1. A cooperative or coordinated effort on the part of a group of persons acting together as a team or in the interest of a common cause.
